ingredients: Wheat Flour (wheat flour, niacin, reduced iron, thiamin mononitrate, riboflavin, folic acid), Salt, Vegetable Oil (high oleic safflower, high oleic soybean, high oleic sunflower, high oleic canola and/or canola oil). Contains less than 2% of: Dried Parmesan Cheese (part skim milk, cheese cultures, salt, enzymes), Yeast, Sugar, Fumaric Acid, Whey, Butter, Modified Food Starch, Buttermilk, Sodium Phosphate, Silicon Dioxide (anticaking agent), Annatto Extract (color).
